<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT60">
<l>āṭpārt tuḻitaruvāy kaṇṭuko ḷeṉṟuniṉ</l>
<l>tāṭpārt tuḻitaruvēṉ taṉmaiyai kēṭpārk</l>
<l>karumporuḷāy niṉṟa varaṅkaṉē yuṉṉai</l>
<l>virumpuvatē viḷḷēṉ maṉam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who wander about looking for servants!</l>
<l>Always see the nature of me who wander about looking for [Your] feet.</l>
<l>O You from Raṅgam who become a hard[-to-find] meaning to those who listen!</l>
<l>I will not leave off desiring You [in my] heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
